      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait caffeine?? wont that make my blood pressure go way up though? i thought that was the opposite of what i need. and i'm kinda feeling a bit lightheaded and dizzy right now because i missed the dose, so i'm worried about my levels being too low. wouldn't taking the two pills be a more direct way to make sure i'm back on track quickly?",
